1
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:16,580
Xiaoxue.

2
00:00:16,580 --> 00:00:17,301
Mr. Gu.

3
00:00:17,740 --> 00:00:18,661
Where are you going?

4
00:00:19,220 --> 00:00:20,740
Young Master Yan just finished drinking.

5
00:00:20,740 --> 00:00:22,100
I'm going to help him clean up.

6
00:00:23,540 --> 00:00:25,141
I was wondering where the bottle went.

7
00:00:25,141 --> 00:00:26,461
Turns out he drank it.

8
00:00:30,380 --> 00:00:31,820
What's that on your neck?

9
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:36,740
I must have bumped it just now.

10
00:00:43,780 --> 00:00:45,100
Mr. Gu,

11
00:00:45,100 --> 00:00:46,981
if you're done, I'll be on my way.

12
00:00:56,701 --> 00:00:58,661
[Ji Xiaoxue's real name is Liu.]

13
00:00:58,820 --> 00:01:01,021
[Her mother died when she was six.]

14
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:02,701
[She was sent to an orphanage.]

15
00:01:02,981 --> 00:01:03,580
Okay.

16
00:01:04,181 --> 00:01:05,060
I see.

17
00:01:23,981 --> 00:01:24,780
Ji Xiaoxue.

18
00:01:26,381 --> 00:01:27,181
Mr Jing.

19
00:01:27,981 --> 00:01:29,101
Where did you go?

20
00:01:29,580 --> 00:01:31,060
I went to throw away the trash.

21
00:01:31,940 --> 00:01:33,300
No wonder I didn't see you

22
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:34,181
in my brother's room.

23
00:01:35,341 --> 00:01:37,140
Young Master Yan just said he wanted to take a walk,

24
00:01:37,140 --> 00:01:38,300
so I went with him.

25
00:01:38,420 --> 00:01:39,660
We're in the garden.

26
00:01:47,261 --> 00:01:48,461
Where's the brooch I gave you?

27
00:01:51,940 --> 00:01:53,020
Where's my brooch?

28
00:01:53,020 --> 00:01:53,580
Right.

29
00:01:53,580 --> 00:01:55,181
How come my brooch is missing?

30
00:01:55,341 --> 00:01:56,940
I don't know if it was just over there.

31
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:58,500
It's with me.

32
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:02,500
How could it be with you?

33
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:27,661
I found it at the entrance to my brother's room.

34
00:02:30,541 --> 00:02:32,020
So it fell there.

35
00:02:39,221 --> 00:02:41,900
Don't lose it again.

36
00:02:53,661 --> 00:02:55,061
Young Master Yan, you're here.

37
00:02:55,740 --> 00:02:57,381
Your treasures have arrived.

38
00:02:57,381 --> 00:02:58,541
I'm admiring them.

39
00:02:58,941 --> 00:02:59,541
Nice.

40
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:01,740
Pick one for me.

41
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:04,261
I... I don't know how to pick.

42
00:03:04,261 --> 00:03:05,701
I can't even understand this.

43
00:03:05,860 --> 00:03:07,140
Just pick the one you like.

44
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:09,860
Just pick one you like.

45
00:03:10,981 --> 00:03:12,180
I'll go to the bathroom.

46
00:03:12,620 --> 00:03:13,740
Do you need help?

47
00:03:31,061 --> 00:03:32,580
Have a seat, Miss.

48
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:36,340
How's the company doing?

49
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:39,900
Miss Xia handed over the Hongbin Real Estate Project

50
00:03:39,900 --> 00:03:40,941
to Gu Chengjing.

51
00:03:41,381 --> 00:03:43,460
Although he's a bit stiff,

52
00:03:43,460 --> 00:03:46,221
many shareholders support him.

53
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:50,140
Don't worry, Sir.

54
00:03:50,661 --> 00:03:53,061
Mr. Gu mentioned your wedding.

55
00:03:53,221 --> 00:03:54,541
I believe those people

56
00:03:54,781 --> 00:03:56,020
know how to choose their side.

57
00:03:58,821 --> 00:03:59,781
Another thing,

58
00:04:01,340 --> 00:04:03,661
she really has nothing to do with Gu Chengjing.

59
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:05,941
She grew up in an orphanage

60
00:04:05,941 --> 00:04:07,541
and then lived alone.

61
00:04:07,661 --> 00:04:08,781
She works several jobs a day.

62
00:04:08,781 --> 00:04:09,501
It's not easy.

63
00:04:09,941 --> 00:04:12,340
She doesn't look like that kind of girl.

64
00:04:14,621 --> 00:04:16,580
You have fair skin.

65
00:04:16,900 --> 00:04:19,460
This ring is a perfect match for you.

66
00:04:24,701 --> 00:04:25,460
Have you made your choice?

67
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:26,980
Yes.

68
00:04:28,381 --> 00:04:30,580
She said she doesn't know anything,

69
00:04:30,821 --> 00:04:31,980
but she picked out

70
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:34,660
the best one in terms of quality and cut.

71
00:04:36,941 --> 00:04:37,660
Wrap it up.

72
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:44,421
Why don't you try it on?

73
00:05:03,181 --> 00:05:03,900
It's for you.

74
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:08,660
Young Master Yan,

75
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:12,660
if it's because of what happened last night,

76
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:14,340
there's really no need to give me a gift.

77
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:15,861
I was drunk last night.

78
00:05:15,861 --> 00:05:16,980
I don't remember anything.

79
00:05:17,701 --> 00:05:19,381
It's not because of what happened last night.

80
00:05:19,900 --> 00:05:20,701
I just...

81
00:05:23,181 --> 00:05:24,780
I just want to give it to you, okay?

82
00:05:26,421 --> 00:05:28,220
But you don't have to give me a ring.

83
00:05:29,421 --> 00:05:30,900
Didn't you pick it yourself?

84
00:05:31,220 --> 00:05:33,061
I thought you were going to give it to Sister Wanqing.

85
00:05:33,061 --> 00:05:33,821
How would I know?

86
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:34,621
Alright.

87
00:05:35,660 --> 00:05:36,861
Just take it.

88
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:38,421
If you don't want it,

89
00:05:41,701 --> 00:05:42,980
just keep it for me.

90
00:05:47,220 --> 00:05:49,261
Your wedding with Wanqing can't be canceled.

91
00:05:49,460 --> 00:05:50,621
It's okay not to cancel it,

92
00:05:51,660 --> 00:05:53,020
but can we postpone it for a few days?

93
00:05:53,181 --> 00:05:53,941
Chengyan,

94
00:05:54,421 --> 00:05:56,061
do you know what's going on?

95
00:05:56,181 --> 00:05:57,861
Your wedding is very important.

96
00:05:58,340 --> 00:05:59,181
After your father's death,

97
00:05:59,540 --> 00:06:00,340
your mother,

98
00:06:01,381 --> 00:06:02,061
no,

99
00:06:03,020 --> 00:06:04,181
Chengjing's mother

100
00:06:04,621 --> 00:06:05,861
has been pushing Chengjing

101
00:06:05,980 --> 00:06:07,140
to take the position of chairman.

102
00:06:07,261 --> 00:06:08,861
I can only let you compete fairly.

103
00:06:09,301 --> 00:06:11,220
I want you

104
00:06:11,660 --> 00:06:13,220
to take over our family business.

105
00:06:13,741 --> 00:06:14,701
Don't you want to?

106
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:15,780
I...

107
00:06:19,181 --> 00:06:20,140
I do.

108
00:06:21,861 --> 00:06:23,540
I won't let my father's business

109
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:25,381
fall into the hands of others.

110
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:27,861
But...

111
00:06:28,261 --> 00:06:29,100
But what?

112
00:06:32,621 --> 00:06:35,460
Chengyan, you're close to Xiaoxue.

113
00:06:36,381 --> 00:06:37,340
Don't forget

114
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:39,381
Chengjing found her for you.

115
00:06:39,821 --> 00:06:41,301
Don't you have any concerns?

116
00:06:41,580 --> 00:06:43,421
Chengjing has found me many.

117
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:45,381
I think Xiaoxue is different.

118
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:47,301
How is she different?

119
00:06:47,501 --> 00:06:49,301
She's just an ordinary girl.

120
00:06:51,701 --> 00:06:53,061
Don't you think

121
00:06:53,741 --> 00:06:54,980
Xiaoxue is special?

122
00:06:57,861 --> 00:06:58,660
Cheng Yan,

123
00:06:59,660 --> 00:07:00,660
what are you talking about?

124
00:07:03,140 --> 00:07:03,861
Nothing.

125
00:07:04,220 --> 00:07:05,540
I just want you to rest assured.

126
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:07,861
I will definitely keep Gu's business

127
00:07:08,181 --> 00:07:09,941
in the hands of Gu's family.

128
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:15,701
The wedding is coming up.

129
00:07:15,701 --> 00:07:16,900
You don't care about it at all.

130
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:17,980
You don't prepare anything.

131
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:19,701
If you don't want to marry me,

132
00:07:19,701 --> 00:07:20,861
just tell me.

133
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:24,980
I don't want to be embarrassed.

134
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:29,741
I...

135
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:35,460
Young Master Yan,

136
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:37,660
I got the ring you bought for Miss Xia.

137
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:43,861
Miss Xia, here you are.

138
00:07:47,381 --> 00:07:48,980
I'll leave you two to it.

139
00:07:58,261 --> 00:08:00,181
Is this really for me?

140
00:08:07,220 --> 00:08:08,340
It's so pretty!

141
00:08:09,941 --> 00:08:11,340
I was wrong about you.

142
00:08:11,701 --> 00:08:13,540
I thought you didn't prepare anything.

143
00:08:18,501 --> 00:08:19,460
Don't worry.

144
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:21,701
Our wedding will be held as scheduled.

145
00:08:29,301 --> 00:08:30,260
It's so late.

146
00:08:30,781 --> 00:08:31,580
How about

147
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:33,860
I stay here?

148
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:35,740
Okay.

149
00:08:36,661 --> 00:08:37,500
I have something to do.

150
00:08:37,901 --> 00:08:39,141
I'll be busy for a while.

151
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:40,661
I'll go wash up.

152
00:08:51,620 --> 00:08:52,340
Come in.

153
00:08:55,141 --> 00:08:55,980
Miss Xia.

154
00:08:58,740 --> 00:09:01,301
Chengyan, you went to the study so early.

155
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:03,220
Didn't you sleep well last night?

156
00:09:03,661 --> 00:09:04,541
Give me a bath.

157
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:05,620
I'll do it.

158
00:09:10,061 --> 00:09:12,260
I'll go get the water ready.

159
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:16,380
Chengyan,

160
00:09:16,620 --> 00:09:18,541
after your bath, we'll go to the wedding dress shop.

161
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:19,580
What do you think?

162
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:21,701
Do you like a grand wedding dress

163
00:09:21,701 --> 00:09:22,740
or a simple one?

164
00:09:24,021 --> 00:09:24,701
Both are fine.

165
00:09:25,701 --> 00:09:27,220
Young Master Yan, the water is ready.

166
00:09:28,141 --> 00:09:28,901
Let's go.

167
00:09:30,021 --> 00:09:31,380
Let Xiaoxue do it.

168
00:09:31,580 --> 00:09:32,941
You go get cleaned up.

169
00:09:40,021 --> 00:09:40,781
Xiaoxue,

170
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:43,980
hurry up.

171
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:46,781
Okay.

172
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:54,340
Mr. Gu, Miss Xia,

173
00:09:54,661 --> 00:09:55,620
your wedding is coming up.

174
00:09:55,941 --> 00:09:58,100
I've prepared the latest styles for you.

175
00:09:58,701 --> 00:09:59,901
But Mr. Gu's suit

176
00:09:59,901 --> 00:10:01,141
may take two more days.

177
00:10:01,941 --> 00:10:02,740
It doesn't matter.

178
00:10:03,421 --> 00:10:05,421
I'm here mainly to accompany her to choose the wedding dress.

179
00:10:34,781 --> 00:10:35,580
Chengyan,

180
00:10:36,901 --> 00:10:38,421
which one do you think is good?

181
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:42,260
This one.

182
00:10:44,021 --> 00:10:45,620
This one is a little too plain.

183
00:10:45,701 --> 00:10:46,661
I don't like it.

184
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:48,460
I think this one is good.

185
00:10:48,661 --> 00:10:49,460
What do you think?

186
00:10:52,701 --> 00:10:53,580
What do you think?
